      • setProfile

        public static boolean setProfile(org.bukkit.inventory.meta.ItemMeta headMeta,
                                 UUID uuid,
                                 String texture)
        Set a profile field in the supplied item meta using a UUID and Texture string
        Parameters:
        headMeta - the item meta to apply the profile on
        uuid - A UUID to be associated with this profile and texture
        texture - The Base64-encoded Texture-URL tags.
        Returns:
        True: the profile was successfully set. False: the profile could not be set.

      • getProfilePlayer

        public static org.bukkit.OfflinePlayer getProfilePlayer(org.bukkit.inventory.meta.SkullMeta headMeta)
        Infers an Owning Player (OfflinePlayer) from the internal profile field information using the UUID. This is equivalent to Bukkit.getOfflinePlayer(ProfileUtils.getProfileUUID(...)).
        Parameters:
        headMeta - the item meta for the head to check
        Returns:
        The OfflinePlayer, or null if no profile was found.
        See Also:
        getProfileUUID(org.bukkit.inventory.meta.SkullMeta)
